src:
Jeongmin releases MV for his New title track " Why "
02 Nov 2019, 22:24 by kpoplovermay
Former Boyfriend member Jeongmin, is Back! with a MV for his New title track " Why "



Which is off his newly released 2nd Single album titled " Off The Record " :



The mv is also on the Super Sound Bugs channel & on music streaming sites like Melon etc.
Check out the quirky sweet MV above, and let us know what you think in the comments below.
